	<p>Kuipp will not sell, trade, send, or transfer your personal information to any external third parties. Please note that this does not include trusted third parties who help us in the operation of our Services, conducting our business operations, or providing additional services to you. We may only share or disclose your information with your consent, such as with the usage of third party clients to access your account. Kuipp may share or disclose your non-private, aggregated or otherwise non-personal information, such as your public questions, answers, or comments to answers.</p>

